short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hide videos from blacklisted YouTube channels.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you tired of seen unwanted YouTube channels? With this plug in you can now blacklist them and never see them again in your searches or recommendations. 

The extension is really simple to use. Just type the name of the channel and forget about it (you can always bring it back if you want).

Help me improving this project here: https://github.com/FedericoGentile/youtube-channels-blacklist
